<view class="page tier-template-page"><view class="form-header"><view class="form-header-title">公里阶梯价模板</view><view class="form-header-desc">小板线路可根据运送公里数设置分段阶梯价，便于系统精确报价。</view></view><view class="section"><view class="section-title">新建价格模板</view><view class="field"><text class="label">模板名称 <text class="required">*</text></text><input class="input" placeholder="例如: 华东近郊阶梯报价" placeholder-style="color:#9ca3af" value="{{a}}" bindinput="{{b}}"/></view><view class="field"><view class="row-between align-center" style="margin-bottom:12rpx"><text class="label" style="margin-bottom:0">分段阶梯规则 <text class="required">*</text></text><text class="text-link" bindtap="{{c}}">+ 新增区间</text></view><view wx:for="{{d}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:key="h" class="tier-rule-row"><view class="row align-center"><input class="input tier-input" type="number" placeholder="起运(km)" value="{{item.a}}" bindinput="{{item.b}}"/><text class="connector-txt">至</text><input class="input tier-input" type="number" placeholder="送达(km)" value="{{item.c}}" bindinput="{{item.d}}"/><text class="unit-txt">公里,</text><input class="input price-input-mini" type="digit" placeholder="元/km" value="{{item.e}}" bindinput="{{item.f}}"/><text class="delete-rule-btn" bindtap="{{item.g}}">×</text></view></view></view><button class="primary-btn animate-btn w-full" loading="{{e}}" bindtap="{{f}}"> 保存并添加价格模板 </button></view><view class="section" style="margin-top:30rpx"><view class="section-title">已有价格模板 ({{g}})</view><view wx:if="{{h}}" class="empty"> 暂无已保存的阶梯价模板 </view><view wx:else class="templates-list"><view wx:for="{{i}}" wx:for-item="t" wx:key="c" class="template-item-card"><view class="template-name font-bold">{{t.a}}</view><view class="template-rules-summary"><view wx:for="{{t.b}}" wx:for-item="rule" wx:key="d" class="rule-summary-row"> · {{rule.a}} - {{rule.b}} 公里: <text class="price-hl font-bold">{{rule.c}}元/公里</text></view></view></view></view></view></view>